what to be used for 
Features
Add Patient: Add a new patient with their details.
Display Patients: List all registered patients.
Add Doctor: Add a doctor with their specialization and availability.
Display Doctors: List all available doctors.
Search Doctor: Search for a doctor by ID.
Schedule Appointment: Schedule an appointment between a patient and a doctor.
Process Appointment: Process the next appointment in the queue.
Instructions
Compile and run the program.
Enter your choice based on the menu options.
For adding patients and doctors, provide the necessary details.
Schedule and process appointments to simulate the operations of a hospital management system.
